title: Hasina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Indian, Fast food, Take-out, Mexican, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Opened in Sept 2012, this fast food eatery makes primarily Indian food with some Mexican and fusion. Has around 8 vegan main, 4 vegetarian mains, and a few vegan starters. Diners can watch the food being prepared behind the counter. Cozy, dark brown seats give the place a lounge feel.
